IRS990.MissionDesc: TO DISSEMINATE ENVIRONMENTAL SOLUTIONS TO EDUCATE, INSPIRE, AND EQUIP PEOPLE TOWARD EFFECTIVE ACTION, TO DEVELOP AND SPREAD MODEL ECONOMIC STRATEGIES THAT CONSERVE BIOLOGICAL AND CULTURAL DIVERSITY, AND TO PROMOTE UNDERSTANDING OF THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN HUMANS AND NATURE.
IRS990.Desc: INDIGENEITY PROGRAM - THE PROGRAM MISSION IS TO PROMOTE INDIGENOUS ENVIRONMENTAL AND SOCIAL JUSTICE LEADERS BY CREATING A CULTURAL BRIDGE AND PUBLIC EDUCATION OUTLETS THROUGH VALUABLE INITIATIVES INCLUDING THE INDIGENOUS FORUM, RIGHTS OF NATURE, MEDIA AND INDIGENOUS EDUCATIONAL CURRICULA AND MATERIALS.NUMBER OF PEOPLE REACHED: A POTENTIAL AUDIENCE REACH OF 1.2 MILLION THROUGH BIONEERS.ORG UNIQUE VISITORS, NATIONAL BIONEERS CONFERENCE ATTENDEES EXPOSURE, LOCAL EVENTS AND ACTIVE SOCIAL MEDIA ENGAGEMENT, WEBSITE, TEK INTENSIVES AND DISTRIBUTION OF EDUCATIONAL MATERIALS.

ProgSrvcAccomActy2Grp.Desc: BIONEERS CONFERENCE - THE BIONEERS "HEADWATERS" CONFERENCE IS A PRE-EMINENT LEADING-EDGE FORUM WHERE SOCIAL AND SCIENTIFIC INNOVATORS FOCUS ON SOLUTIONS INSPIRED BY NATURE AND HUMAN INGENUITY.NUMBER OF PEOPLE REACHED: A POTENTIAL ANNUAL AUDIENCE REACH OF 1.2 MILLION THROUGH BIONEERS.ORG UNIQUE VISITORS, NATIONAL BIONEERS CONFERENCE ATTENDEES, LOCAL EVENTS AND ACTIVE SOCIAL MEDIA ENGAGEMENT; ESTIMATED TOTAL REGULAR REACH OF 65 MILLION VIA RADIO/TV; RADIO SERIES BUILT FROM CONFERENCE CONTENT IS APPROXIMATELY 125 US STATIONS AS WELL AS 200 REPEATER STATIONS FOR A TOTAL OF 325 STATIONS. VIDEO DISTRIBUTED VIA LINKTV AND OTHER BROADCAST METHODS. TENS OF MILLIONS VIA CONFERENCE VIDEO DISTRIBUTED VIA SOCIAL MEDIA AND YOUTUBE (APPROXIMATELY 240,000+ FOLLOWERS ON ALL SOCIAL PLATFORMS; VIDEO CONTENT ON SOCIAL PLATFORMS INCLUDING YOUTUBE AND FACEBOOK HAVE RECEIVED OVER 13,275,000 VIEWS.) MONTHLY WEBSITE TRAFFIC IS AT 3X HISTORICAL AVERAGES, WITH AN AVERAGE OF 100K VISITORS/MONTH.

ProgSrvcAccomActy3Grp.Desc: BIONEERS RESILIENT COMMUNITIES NETWORK/LOCALIZATION/DNM/F&F (INCLUDES ASPECTS OF BIONEERS LEARNING, POLLINATOR/BEAMING, LOCALIZATION AND RESTORATIVE FOOD SYSTEMS) - AN INNOVATIVE BIONEERS COLLABORATIVE PROJECT TO RECONCILE NATURE AND CULTURES. ACTIVITIES INCLUDE BIONEERS LEARNING, COMMUNITY RESILIENCE, ENGAGEMENT OF A "LEARNING NETWORK", LOCALIZATION, DNM AND RESTORATIVE FOOD SYSTEMS.NUMBER OF PEOPLE REACHED: A POTENTIAL AUDIENCE REACH OF 1.2 MILLION THROUGH BIONEERS.ORG UNIQUE VISITORS, NATIONAL CONFERENCE ATTENDEES EXPOSURE, LOCAL EVENTS AND ACTIVE SOCIAL MEDIA ENGAGEMENT, WEBSITE AND DISTRIBUTION OF EDUCATIONAL MATERIALS. THIS PROGRAM HAS UNLIMITED POTENTIAL TO HELP BUILD COMMUNITY RESILIENCE FROM THE GROUND UP.

ProgSrvcAccomActyOtherGrp.Desc: ELRF - (A RE-GRANTING FUND) THE FUND AWARDS GRANTS AND FELLOWSHIPS TO WOMEN-LED ORGANIZATIONS AND INDIVIDUALS ACROSS DIVERSE FIELDS WHO MAKE INNOVATIVE CONTRIBUTIONS.IT HELPS LEVERAGE UNDER-RECOGNIZED AND OFTEN GRASSROOTS WOMEN AND GROUPS TO OBTAIN EXPOSURE, CONNECTIONS AND FUNDING. INCLUDES INDIGIGIVING ACTIVITY.NUMBER OF PEOPLE SERVED/AFFECTED/ATTENDING/ETC.: 45 INDIVIDUALS AND 62 ORGANIZATIONS THAT SERVE THOUSANDS OF CONSTITUENTS. THIS PROGRAM HAS UNLIMITED POTENTIAL THROUGH THE GRANTS AND FELLOWSHIPS PROVIDED.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: UNDER SECTION 501(C)(3) OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE, THE ORGANIZATION IS EXEMPT FROM TAXES ON INCOME OTHER THAN UNRELATED BUSINESS INCOME. HOWEVER, TAXES ON UNRELATED BUSINESS INCOME, IF ANY, ARE REPORTED WHEN PAID. THE ORGANIZATION DID NOT INCUR TAXES ON UNRELATED BUSINESS INCOME FOR THE YEARS ENDED MARCH 31, 2023 AND 2022. THE ORGANIZATION UTILIZES THE ACCOUNTING REQUIREMENTS ASSOCIATED WITH UNCERTAINTY IN INCOME TAXES USING THE PROVISIONS OF FINANCIAL ACCOUNTING STANDARDS BOARD (FASB) ASC 740, INCOME TAXES. USING THAT GUIDANCE, TAX POSITIONS INITIALLY NEED TO BE RECOGNIZED IN THE FINANCIAL STATEMENTS WHEN IT IS MORE-LIKELY-THAN-NOT THE POSITIONS WILL BE SUSTAINED UPON EXAMINATION BY THE TAX AUTHORITIES. IT ALSO PROVIDES GUIDANCE FOR DE-RECOGNITION, CLASSIFICATION, INTEREST AND PENALTIES, ACCOUNTING IN INTERIM PERIODS, DISCLOSURE AND TRANSITION. AS OF MARCH 31, 2023 AND 2022, THE ORGANIZATION HAS NO UNCERTAIN TAX PROVISIONS THAT QUALIFY FOR RECOGNITION OR DISCLOSURE IN THE FINANCIAL STATEMENTS.
